    "Should explain `getuigen` as the witnesses / baptismal sponsors (FAN-club figures worth researching), and `soon van` as 'son of'.",
    "Should keep the names in their original Dutch form (Pieter, Jan, Maria, Cornelis, Aaltje), not anglicize them."
